Package: rsurv
Type: Package
Title: Random Generation of Survival Times
Version: 0.0.0.9999
Authors@R: c(
    person("Devin", "Incerti", , "devin.incerti@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Randomly draw survival times from survival curves without making 
    parametric assumptions in an efficient manner. Each individual can have
    their own survival function and code is written in C++ to ensure that all 
    random sampling is vectorized.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: 
    data.table,
    Rcpp (>= 1.0.6)
Suggests:
    knitr
LinkingTo: Rcpp
URL: https://github.com/hesim-dev/rsurv, http://hesim-dev.github.io/rsurv/
BugReports: https://github.com/hesim-dev/rsurv/issues
VignetteBuilder: knitr
